### Save AI History Entry
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation SaveAIHistory($input: SaveAIHistoryInput!) { saveAIHistory(input: $input) }",
  "variables": {
    "input": {
      "userId": "abc123",
      "type": "summary",
      "input": {
        "jobDescription": "Senior frontend role using React and GraphQL"
      },
      "output": {
        "summary": "A senior role focusing on React and GraphQL frontend work."
      }
    }
  }
}


### Fetch All AI History for User
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query AIHistory($userId: ID!) { aiHistory(userId: $userId) { id type createdAt output } }",
  "variables": {
    "userId": "abc123"
  }
}
